msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../C/cookbook.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from amateur electronics and radio] A book of small code segments that the "
"reader can use to do various :ref:`magic` things in programs. Cookbooks, "
"slavishly followed, can lead one into :ref:`voodoo-programming`\\, but are "
"useful for hackers trying to :ref:`monkey-up` small programs in unknown "
"languages. This function is analogous to the role of phrasebooks in human "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"[アマチュア電子工学と無線から] 読者がプログラムでさまざまな\\ :ref:`magic`\\ "
"なことをするのに使える小さなコード断片の本。クックブックは、盲目的に従うと\\ :ref:`voodoo-programming`\\ "
"に導きかねませんが、未知の言語で小さなプログラムを\\ :ref:`monkey-up`\\ "
"しようとするハッカーには有用です。この機能は、人間の言語におけるフレーズ集の役割に類似しています。"
